<br>
Does it generate some bad ass aggro yes it does.  Hence the AA points needed for SCS 1,2 and 3.<br>
<br>
To increase the mana use on the spell you need SCM 3.<br>
<br>
Do you get some nice eye candy crits?  Hell yes.<br>
<br>
Now lets look at focus effects, everyone seems to be concentrating solely on PoP focus effects, lets just take a look at VT focus items.  Not even going to mention &quot;XXX&quot; of Secrets items.  Just the other more common and easier to get things for a wizard.<br>
<br>
Ring of Flamewarding  26% extra damage on Fire nukes<br>
Robe of Luring Shadows 23% MP I think.<br>
Shade Stone Amulet  15 or 20% Spell haste<br>
<br>
All 3 of these are pretty common drops there.  So these are pretty simple items to get.  <br>
<br>
Now combine with AA points and Rizonia's Song, and you are talking some major damage.<br>
<br>
As to aggro I would rarely ever get aggro with SoS on raid boss mobs or even in Exp groups.  And yes I would pretty much chain cast nukes.  However there was always the odd mob that no matter whjen I nuked it, it would summon and kill me in PoS.  Go figure.<br>
<br>
